commit.message:
lib1funcs.asm, [...]: GCC, not GNU CC.

	* config/v850/lib1funcs.asm, config/v850/rtems.h,
	config/v850/v850-c.c, config/v850/v850-protos.h,
	config/v850/v850.c, config/v850/v850.h, config/v850/v850.md:
	GCC, not GNU CC.

From-SVN: r64296
